reviews.text: Their satay beef and egg sandwich is must try. Ask for the bread to be toasted. The BBQ pork bun is also great. The shop is very small, there is only one table and the rest are bar seats facing the wall. The service is also pretty good considering the size. Price is very reasonable too.
this place is so good!!!!!! BBQ pork egg sandwich was out of this world w that honey glazed bun and sunny side egg oozing. milk tea smells amazing also

Decent cup of tea. The pineapple bun with eggs is also surprisingly great. The bun is toasted and warm. That is much better than the other places nearby. The only downside is that the table is small and the seat is relatively tall. It is more like a stand and eat place. Put those things aside, it still worth all those inconvenience.

Actually the shop name means “My cup of tea”.

Their chilled classic Hong Kong style milk tea in glass bottle ($30) is excellent. Be environmental friendly, return the glass bottle (rinsed) to get $2 back.
Excellent Hong Kong style milk tea. We particularly like the sandwich with egg and  barbecue pork. Friendly service. P.S. Bring your own cup if you prefer to not use the takeaway paper cups.

reviews.text: 童年的地方🤓

Their satay beef and egg sandwich is must try. Ask for the bread to be toasted. The BBQ pork bun is also great. The shop is very small, there is only one table and the rest are bar seats facing the wall. The service is also pretty good considering the size. Price is very reasonable too.

茶底唔錯，食品又好食
扣剩一星，好似好環保，用紙飲管，但堂食都用即棄膠杯囉！

食物新鮮制作 好味
奶茶甘香 入口幼滑 茶底再厚啲就更好
位於灣仔的春園街，又拿了金茶王大獎的師傅開設的小店我杯茶，主打港式奶茶 及一些地道的茶餐廳小吃。點了鮮牛肉蛋治烘底 （加$2)，以及凍奶茶，奶茶少冰的緣故未到沒有因此變得淡口，茶底亦沒有苦澀味，入口有回甘！加了煉奶，甜度亦都不會太過分。推薦給遊客來一試！

Reasonable price, wide variety of fast serving  food option.
物有所值，服務迅速。
食物款式選擇多，如咖喱豬扒炒飯及盤菜等。
常餐用生命麵包，而且可選奶油多，有別於一般茶餐廳用又硬又油膩的普通牛油麵包。
迷你盤菜夠熱，但係太多燒味
